These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-1::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  mechanic, nurse
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skiing, water-polo
2 different games are played: poker, monopoly
1. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person playing poker##1
2. the nurse is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Job   | nurse    | mechanic |
| Sport         | water-polo | skiing    |
| Game     | poker     | monopoly      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-2::.
City: san-francisco, colone
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: house, salsa
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, train
1. the person driving the train is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
2. the fan of house is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| City      | colone  | san-francisco   |
| Music-Genre   | salsa | house  |
| Transport     | train   | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: collecting, writing
There are 2 different nationalities: turkish, american
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, zinnia
1. the person who's hobby is writing is in an even position##4
2. the turkish is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| Hobby         | collecting   | writing  |
| Nationality   | american | turkish  |
| Flower         | balloon-flower   | zinnia |

