.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-7::.
There are 2 different nationalities: colombian, german
The people have 2 different jobs:  accountant, dancer
There are 2 different favourite colors: lilac, fuchsia
1. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the accountant##1
2. the person who likes lilac is on the left or right of the person who likes fuchsia##3
3. the colombian is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Nationality    | german | colombian     |
| Job     | dancer | accountant |
| Color   | fuchsia | lilac    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-8::.
