.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-11::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  chef, coach
There are 2 different favourite beverages: fanta, almond-milk
2 different pets are kept: turtle, snake
1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
2. the person drinking almond-milk is in an odd position##4
3. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the coach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |  2   |
| Job           | coach     | chef |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | fanta  |
| Pet     | snake      | turtle |

