.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-15::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: collecting, rock-climbing
The people have 2 different jobs:  journalist, analyst
There 2 different types of food: peas, radish
1. the person eating radish is on the left of the person eating peas##1
2. the journalist is on the left of the analyst##1
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | collecting |
| Job   | journalist     | analyst     |
| Food           | radish          | peas     |

